Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:00.89,0:00:02.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,突然被赋予死神的能力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:03.08,0:00:03.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从那天起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:03.99,0:00:05.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的世界就改变了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:06.00,0:00:07.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死神代行黑崎一护
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:07.96,0:00:09.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了保护重要的同伴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:09.92,0:00:11.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,深沉的信念爆发
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:11.96,0:00:14.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,挥动起灵魂之刃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:04.37,0:02:05.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是好久没见了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:06.42,0:02:07.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这个样子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:08.60,0:02:10.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你现在究竟是何种心境啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.49,0:02:12.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,狛村
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.94,0:02:17.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么...你还能笑得出来 蓝染
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.96,0:02:20.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你欺骗并背叛了我们所有人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.16,0:02:22.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我绝对不会原谅你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.32,0:02:26.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有你也是 东仙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.56,0:02:46.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对...对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.55,0:02:49.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没想到这里会有人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.05,0:02:50.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在这边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.89,0:02:56.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.16,0:02:58.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.99,0:03:00.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没想到你会在那里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.21,0:03:04.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫东仙要 请多指教
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.85,0:03:09.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过话说回来\N你隐藏自己的气息还真有一手啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.38,0:03:11.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我虽然看不见
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.99,0:03:14.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是从来不会察觉不到对方的气息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.01,0:03:19.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,狛村...你是狛村吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.05,0:03:21.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好久不见了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.11,0:03:25.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗 你也加入护廷十三队了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.21,0:03:28.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以的话 你早点来我们队上吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.37,0:03:30.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们队长是一位相当出色的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.52,0:03:32.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也一定会喜欢他的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.00,0:03:35.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就是狛村吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.00,0:03:37.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我听东仙说起过你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.06,0:03:40.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请多指教
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.56,0:03:44.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是五番队副队长 蓝染惣右介
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.35,0:03:49.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你为什么要成为死神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.23,0:03:54.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想向救过我的人报恩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.92,0:03:57.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,报恩吗 很像是你的作风啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.60,0:04:00.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你又是为了什么呢 东仙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.82,0:04:01.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.28,0:04:03.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是因为...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.68,0:04:25.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,东仙 你还有什么要辩解的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.06,0:04:28.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一句...都没有吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.99,0:04:31.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真遗憾 东仙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.29,0:04:35.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卍解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.30,0:04:40.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.88,0:04:44.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蓝染还在...东仙的旁边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.75,0:04:47.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,破道之九十
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.28,0:04:50.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黑棺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.96,0:05:05.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同是队长级别的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.11,0:05:10.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然会这么不堪一击
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.53,0:05:14.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,镜花水月的完全催眠是绝对全面的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.17,0:05:16.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使知道自己中了招
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.68,0:05:18.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也没有逃开的方法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.51,0:05:22.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,九十番台咏唱破弃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.36,0:05:23.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是够恐怖的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.78,0:05:26.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您是从什么时候开始会用这招的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.53,0:05:29.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 失败了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.06,0:05:32.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还没能使出原本破坏力的三分之一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.68,0:05:36.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,九十番台果然不易使用啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.76,0:05:38.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.10,0:05:40.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.52,0:05:43.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟你们的对话似乎还未完
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.07,0:05:45.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黑崎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.55,0:05:48.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们...别过来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.60,0:05:59.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,朽木
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.95,0:06:03.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀呀 你们可不准插手哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.44,0:06:09.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,井上 石田
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.39,0:06:13.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好惊人的灵压啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.62,0:06:17.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,朽木露琪亚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.94,0:06:20.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当你在现世被发现的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.37,0:06:23.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就马上采取了行动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.15,0:06:26.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是四十六室的屠杀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.35,0:06:35.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们从勇音那里听到的 恐怕是这样的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.52,0:06:39.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"蓝染惣右介假装被杀 并藏匿行踪"
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.41,0:06:43.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"其后杀害了四十六室"
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.00,0:06:46.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是那其实是错误的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.84,0:06:51.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你被发现以后 我马上就杀了四十六室
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.82,0:06:54.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并对中央地下\N议事堂的所有人都施了镜花水月
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.01,0:07:00.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我设下了四十六室还活着的假象
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.21,0:07:06.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且我们三人中\N一般有一人会留守在地下议事堂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.98,0:07:11.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至今为止一直假扮四十六室
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.00,0:07:14.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并下达着所有的命令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.72,0:07:17.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了确保将你捕获
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.96,0:07:20.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我将前去捉捕你的人换成了六番队的那两人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.48,0:07:23.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了让你远离人类
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.20,0:07:26.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我下令将义骸及时进行了破坏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.82,0:07:29.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了使你的魂魄能完全蒸发
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.68,0:07:32.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以便从中取出"崩玉"
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.68,0:07:36.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我下令使用双殛将你处决
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.20,0:07:40.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们三人全都离开地下议事堂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.22,0:07:44.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就只有包括\N第二次队长会议在内的前后几小时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.06,0:07:50.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那之后我就马上装死并潜伏在地下议事堂中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.33,0:07:57.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我推断\N由于你们的行动有可能会使处刑失败
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.97,0:08:05.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要将直接埋入\N魂魄里的异物质取出 只有两个方法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.64,0:08:08.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一种就是如双殛那样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.10,0:08:11.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用超高的热破坏能力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.66,0:08:14.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将魂魄这个外壳蒸发 取出异物质
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.36,0:08:18.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或者使用其他方法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.81,0:08:20.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直接介入魂魄组成
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.28,0:08:22.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,强制其分离
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.15,0:08:27.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果万一双殛处刑失败的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.69,0:08:31.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就必须找到另一方法才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.53,0:08:34.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为此 我需要的是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.97,0:08:39.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,地下议事堂的大灵书回廊里所收集的情报
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.85,0:08:45.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我对浦原喜助过去的研究\N一一进行了详细的调查
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.34,0:08:50.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为 向魂魄中埋入异物质\N就是他研究出来的技术
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.71,0:08:56.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因此我想 要将其取出的技术
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.95,0:09:00.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定也藏在他过去的研究中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.19,0:09:01.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:03.70,0:09:06.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是...答案
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.32,0:09:26.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是让我吃惊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.29,0:09:29.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来是这么小的东西啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.64,0:09:31.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是"崩玉"
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.97,0:09:39.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魂魄本身毫发无伤吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.84,0:09:42.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是了不起的技术
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.18,0:09:45.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是遗憾的是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.69,0:09:47.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你对我已经
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.34,0:09:49.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有用了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.67,0:09:51.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杀了她 银
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.18,0:09:56.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真没办法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.97,0:10:00.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,射杀 神枪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.68,0:10:16.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥...哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.09,0:10:22.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.74,0:10:25.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.94,0:10:26.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.81,0:10:29.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么要救我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.36,0:10:39.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们上 兕丹坊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.20,0:10:40.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.09,0:10:43.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,散落的野兽之骨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.25,0:10:46.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尖塔 红晶 钢铁之车轮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.41,0:10:49.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,动则成风 静如晴空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.22,0:10:52.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,击枪的音色充满虚城
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.02,0:10:56.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,破道之六十三 雷吼炮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.55,0:11:01.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.26,0:11:02.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兕丹坊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:07.28,0:11:10.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这回又是些许久没见的人啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.11,0:11:11.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不准动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.16,0:11:13.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要敢动一下下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.52,0:11:15.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就让你血溅当场
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.87,0:11:18.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.67,0:11:23.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,空鹤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.16,0:11:25.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哟 夜一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.77,0:11:27.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我闲得慌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.84,0:11:30.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以散散步 顺便看看情况
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.77,0:11:40.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀 真够壮观的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.61,0:11:42.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.97,0:11:45.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不准动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.51,0:11:51.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思啊 蓝染队长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.68,0:11:52.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我被抓住了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.11,0:11:56.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到此为止了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.50,0:11:58.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.79,0:12:00.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还不明白吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.99,0:12:02.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们已经...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.84,0:12:05.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无处可逃了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.21,0:12:11.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蓝染
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.85,0:12:13.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蓝染队长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.35,0:12:20.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该结束了 蓝染
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:26.49,0:12:27.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么可笑的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.45,0:12:29.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呵呵 不好意思啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.95,0:12:30.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到时间了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.06,0:12:32.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快离开 碎蜂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.56,0:12:46.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎...怎么可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.13,0:12:54.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"大虚"
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.74,0:12:59.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是合成体吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.14,0:13:01.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那到底是什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.83,0:13:04.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不止 那里面好像还有东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.30,0:13:15.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是遗憾啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.54,0:13:20.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本想让你再抓着我一会儿的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.30,0:13:22.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见了 乱菊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.42,0:13:25.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.55,0:13:33.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想逃走吗 你这个...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.05,0:13:34.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.81,0:13:36.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总队长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.83,0:13:40.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那束光叫作"反膜"
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.17,0:13:44.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是"大虚"在帮助同族时使用的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.67,0:13:47.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被那束光包围后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.25,0:13:53.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,光束的内外将成为\N互相无法干涉的完全隔绝的世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.29,0:13:58.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,曾与"大虚"战斗过的人都知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.39,0:14:01.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那束光降临的瞬间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:01.84,0:14:05.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们就已经无法再触碰到蓝染了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.83,0:14:08.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,东仙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.82,0:14:11.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你给我下来 东仙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.37,0:14:13.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我实在很不解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.62,0:14:15.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你为什么要成为死神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.55,0:14:18.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是为了已故的友人吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.77,0:14:20.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是为了伸张正义的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.66,0:14:24.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的正义消失到哪里去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.33,0:14:26.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是说过吗 狛村
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.48,0:14:29.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呈现在我眼中的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.45,0:14:31.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过是条染血的道路而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.26,0:14:33.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正义就在那里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.99,0:14:37.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我所走的 正是正义之道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.89,0:14:40.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,东仙...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.78,0:14:49.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到你竟然会与"大虚"联手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.08,0:14:54.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你到底是为了什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.46,0:14:55.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了寻求更高处
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.80,0:14:59.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你堕落了吗 蓝染
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.49,0:15:02.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样说也太假清高了吧 浮竹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.62,0:15:06.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从一开始就没有任何人立于天上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.12,0:15:09.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是 我也是 甚至神也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.29,0:15:11.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:12.48,0:15:15.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那令人无法忍受的天之座的空缺将就此结束
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.63,0:15:19.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从今以后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.13,0:15:24.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我将立于天上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.49,0:15:28.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见了 各位死神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.11,0:15:36.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有 再见了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.09,0:15:38.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,旅祸少年
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.94,0:15:43.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作为人类 你确实非常有趣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.61,0:15:52.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,二班和三班去治疗朽木队长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.97,0:15:57.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,七班 十一班和十三班去治疗狛村队长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.94,0:16:00.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿散井副队长的治疗 第六阶段施术完毕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.31,0:16:02.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,八班和九班准备进行移送
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.51,0:16:04.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.31,0:16:06.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是相当重的伤势
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.73,0:16:07.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,动作迅速一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.32,0:16:09.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.25,0:16:11.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.96,0:16:13.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可以啊 现在还在治疗中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.88,0:16:16.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经没事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.41,0:16:18.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们快去救其他人吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.70,0:16:21.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您这样太乱来了啊 狛村队长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.13,0:16:23.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听好了 要轻轻地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.33,0:16:26.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个...伊江村三席
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.73,0:16:27.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们要做些什么呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.27,0:16:30.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们去帮忙治疗旅祸吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.40,0:16:33.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.91,0:16:35.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们应该也明白了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.29,0:16:39.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们可是尸魂界的大恩人啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.86,0:16:40.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.05,0:16:41.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.55,0:16:44.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说回来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.12,0:16:46.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个旅祸的女孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.94,0:16:49.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她那能力到底是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.16,0:16:53.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您辛苦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.99,0:16:56.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卯之花队长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.76,0:17:00.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日番谷队长和雏森副队长的情况怎么样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:01.47,0:17:03.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,暂时是保住性命了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.39,0:17:06.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来就要看他们自己的造化了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.30,0:17:10.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在勇音正在代我进行处理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.14,0:17:12.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有谁没接受治疗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:12.59,0:17:13.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.25,0:17:15.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有朽木队长和旅祸少年没有接受治疗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:17.96,0:17:21.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,旅祸那边似乎用不着帮忙了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.90,0:17:23.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 是吗...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.08,0:17:27.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真是乱来啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.37,0:17:29.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,朽木队长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.07,0:17:36.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,朽木露琪亚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.03,0:17:37.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你来这边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.19,0:17:39.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,朽木队长在叫你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:41.79,0:17:44.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,露琪亚 你在那边吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.34,0:17:50.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 哥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.11,0:17:54.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有话要跟你说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:55.44,0:17:56.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是五十年前的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.28,0:17:58.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很久以前的事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.46,0:18:03.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那一年 就在最初的梅花盛开之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.81,0:18:07.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的妻子去世了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.61,0:18:09.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这我知道的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.89,0:18:10.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绯真嫂子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.46,0:18:14.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥就是因为看中了我长得很像她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.59,0:18:18.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以收我入朽木家做义妹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.94,0:18:19.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是这么听家丁们说的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.80,0:18:28.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 我是曾经命令他们这么跟你说过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.75,0:18:34.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绯真其实是你的姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.56,0:18:41.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绯真死了以后就和你组成了临时家庭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:43.62,0:18:46.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当时 实在是穷得无法生活下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.06,0:18:51.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以将还是婴儿的你给丢弃了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.09,0:18:53.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她是这么跟我说的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.73,0:18:56.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绯真她一直很后悔这么做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:57.74,0:18:59.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她成为我妻子以后的五年间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:00.57,0:19:03.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每天都在寻找着你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.59,0:19:09.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然而第五年的春天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:10.76,0:19:11.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白哉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.57,0:19:14.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请你一定要找到我的妹妹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.97,0:19:17.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到以后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.64,0:19:21.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千万不要告诉她我是她姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:21.43,0:19:23.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到她 然后呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.95,0:19:25.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要告诉她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.37,0:19:30.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是希望白哉你能尽力帮我守护我的妹妹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.90,0:19:35.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我曾丢弃了我的妹妹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:36.21,0:19:36.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绯真
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:38.60,0:19:41.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没有资格被叫姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:42.17,0:19:48.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 请让那孩子叫你哥哥来代替吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:50.75,0:19:53.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第一轮的梅花开了 你看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.81,0:19:58.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直到最后 还跟你撒娇 对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:59.45,0:20:03.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没法报答你对我的爱 对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.09,0:20:07.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,与白哉一起度过的这五年时光
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:07.82,0:20:10.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绯真就如同生活在梦中一般
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:12.09,0:20:12.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白哉...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:21.08,0:20:23.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到你是在第二年
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:25.10,0:20:28.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我马上就将你接入了朽木家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:31.39,0:20:33.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和迎娶绯真时一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:34.23,0:20:40.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,家里人极其反对\N我将流魂街的人带入贵族当中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.51,0:20:43.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说这会败坏朽木家的名声
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:44.02,0:20:46.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我却不顾大家的反对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:47.57,0:20:51.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无论如何 我也想完成我与绯真的约定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.73,0:20:56.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 我违反了规定却是事实
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:57.90,0:21:00.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在父母的墓前发誓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:01.60,0:21:03.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了守住规定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:04.40,0:21:06.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我发誓这是最后一次违反规定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:07.74,0:21:10.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无论今后发生任何事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:10.87,0:21:12.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我都要守住规定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:14.75,0:21:17.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一心只想守住和绯真的约定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:19.07,0:21:22.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而发了两个不该发的誓言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:23.81,0:21:26.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你被决定处刑时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:26.76,0:21:28.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一瞬间变得无法判断
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:30.13,0:21:32.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是要守住与父母定下的遵守规定的誓言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:33.26,0:21:36.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是要守住与绯真的约定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:36.38,0:21:38.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我究竟应该选择哪个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:45.66,0:21:47.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果连我们都无法遵守规定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:48.78,0:21:51.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那还有谁会遵守规定呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:52.61,0:21:55.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我是站在你的立场上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:57.00,0:21:59.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想我也一定会挑战陈规
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:05.66,0:22:06.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黑崎一护
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:08.83,0:22:09.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要多谢你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:13.45,0:22:14.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,露琪亚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:22.54,0:22:23.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:00.72,0:24:03.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夜一 你借给我这些道具
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:03.34,0:24:04.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你到底是放在哪里的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:04.53,0:24:06.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的另一个身份是猫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:06.85,0:24:10.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是有一只机器猫\N有着什么都能放进去的口袋嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:10.80,0:24:11.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和那个是一样的
